title: Cisco Stackwise ring status
agents: snmp
author: Kuhn & Rueß GmbH <info@kuhn-ruess.de>
catalog: hw/network/cisco
license: GPL
distribution: check_mk
description:
 This check monitors the StackWise ring status on Cisco switches
 by reading {cswRingRedundant} from the CISCO-STACKWISE-MIB.

 The service reports {OK} when the ring is redundant (closed loop)
 and {CRIT} when the ring is not redundant, which indicates a broken
 StackWise cable or a failed stack member.

inventory:
 One service is created per stack on devices that expose
 the CISCO-STACKWISE-MIB.
